# progress list

```
1 to 2 weeks per feature phase

phase 1
1 - image segmentation - identify body sections and mark numerically
2 - rotate a torso (generate middle images)



phase 2 
1 - arm rotation and rise for walk sequence
2 - leg movement for walk sequence



phase 3 
1 - put assets together for a complete character face
2- put assets together for a complete dressed character body


phase 4
1 - add character to a scene
2 - animate a character in a scene (simple rotation and walk)

phase 5
1 - add written dialogue to a scene
2 - add 8 bit music

phase 6
1 - add ai dialogue (voiced)


phase 7 
1 - refactor and improve animation


phase 8
1 - add in running and jumping
2 - add in other basic arm movements

```


